text: Novyye Ishly () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kacheganovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 467 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 3 km from Kacheganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Novyye Ishly
